  "logNo": "220537504586",
  "title": "11월11일은 빼빼로데이 ",
  "addDate": "2015. 11. 12.",
  "categoryNo": "43",
  "parentCategoryNo": "1",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=220537504586",
  "html_size": 186047,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view220537504586\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea220537504586\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">안녕하세요</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">요즘 날씨가 다시 조금 따뜻해진거같은데</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">그래도 아침이랑 밤에는 좀 춥더라구요..</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">그러니까 블로그 친구분들 감기 걸리지 않게 옷은 항상 따뜻하게 입구다니세요~ ^^</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">화요일 저녁 진료끝나기 20분전쯤 환자분이 오셔서</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">데스크로 오시더니 </p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\"이거.. 받으세요\" 하시면서 주셨어요</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">담날이 빼빼로 데이라고 오시는 길에 일부러 사오셨다고..</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">감사합니다 ^^</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/sally_friends\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fde37aaa9cb290de.png\" alt=\"sally_friends-5\"></a></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">박스 하나랑 이쁜 하트 4개가 요렇게 같이 있었어요</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151112_31/isuhani_14473384386957d3C7_JPEG/1.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 360px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20151112_31/isuhani_14473384386957d3C7_JPEG/1.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033590F434A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151112_31/isuhani_14473384386957d3C7_JPEG/1.JPG?type=w3\"></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151112_143/isuhani_14473387109630zYFc_JPEG/2.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 360px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20151112_143/isuhani_14473387109630zYFc_JPEG/2.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033590F434A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151112_143/isuhani_14473387109630zYFc_JPEG/2.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151112_182/isuhani_1447338711272dqR8A_JPEG/PB104911.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rheight: 360px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20151112_182/isuhani_1447338711272dqR8A_JPEG/PB104911.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033590F434A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151112_182/isuhani_1447338711272dqR8A_JPEG/PB104911.JPG?type=w3\"></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">하트만봐도 이쁘죠?</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">박스 안에 뭐가 들어있을까요?</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151112_76/isuhani_1447338485757BKc79_JPEG/4.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 360px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20151112_76/isuhani_1447338485757BKc79_JPEG/4.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033590F434A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151112_76/isuhani_1447338485757BKc79_JPEG/4.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">짜잔~~~</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151112_269/isuhani_14473385303536hcGm_JPEG/5.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 360px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20151112_269/isuhani_14473385303536hcGm_JPEG/5.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033590F434A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151112_269/isuhani_14473385303536hcGm_JPEG/5.JPG?type=w3\"></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">이건.. 브라우니 스틱인가? </p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">초코맛도 있구 녹차맛도있구..</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151112_65/isuhani_1447338563210PEKFb_JPEG/6.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 360px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20151112_65/isuhani_1447338563210PEKFb_JPEG/6.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033590F434A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151112_65/isuhani_1447338563210PEKFb_JPEG/6.JPG?type=w3\"></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">브라우니도 참 이쁘고 맛있게&nbsp;생겼어요&nbsp;ㅎㅎ</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">데코가 하트로 되있어요</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">하트뿅뿅~<br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">맛도 짱!</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">촉촉하고 많이 달지도 않고 완전맛있어요 ^^</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/line_characters_in_love\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fa78c6dc40535c86.png\" alt=\"line_characters_in_love-15\"></a>&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">얼굴도 이쁘고 마음씨도 이쁘고</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">우리 환자분들은 다 천사같으신 분들만 있는거같아요 ㅎㅎ</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/sally_friends\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/623edde9f1ac1f76.png\" alt=\"sally_friends-2\"></a></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
